  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "80000011_e00001",
      "play_id": "80000011",
      "scene_id": "80000011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "搀扶！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000011_e00002",
      "play_id": "80000011",
      "scene_id": "80000011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "太监扶刘备同上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000011_e00003",
      "play_id": "80000011",
      "scene_id": "80000011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "恨不得把吴狗顷国灭尽，报弟仇杀孙权方称我的心。陆逊儿用诡计令人可恨，多亏了那赵子龙救驾逃生。烧得孤连营寨七百里整，烧得孤人和马七十余万片甲无存。烧得孤在火焰下四处奔命，烧得孤兵败在白帝城。为此事不由孤我的珠泪滚滚，只觉得心神不定我坐卧不宁。",
      "text_length": 120
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000011_e00004",
      "play_id": "80000011",
      "scene_id": "80000011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "唉，实指望与二弟、三弟报仇，杀得东吴堪堪大败，不想中了陆逊小儿用火之计，烧孤连营七百余里。因此兵败白帝城，身染重病。这几日，常见二弟、三弟，在孤面前，不离左右。大料孤不久于人世了！",
      "text_length": 90
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000011_e00005",
      "play_id": "80000011",
      "scene_id": "80000011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "梦魂间一阵阵心神不稳，见二弟和三弟不离我的身。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000011_e00006",
      "play_id": "80000011",
      "scene_id": "80000011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "哦，二弟来了！啊，二弟！啊，二弟你来啊……",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000011_e00007",
      "play_id": "80000011",
      "scene_id": "80000011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "太监"
      ],
      "text": "启禀主公：我那二千岁不在人世了！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000011_e00008",
      "play_id": "80000011",
      "scene_id": "80000011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "怎么，你那二千岁，他、他、他不在人世了？",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000011_e00009",
      "play_id": "80000011",
      "scene_id": "80000011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "太监"
      ],
      "text": "不在人世了！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000011_e00010",
      "play_id": "80000011",
      "scene_id": "80000011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "哭",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "二弟呀……",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000011_e00011",
      "play_id": "80000011",
      "scene_id": "80000011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "你本是大英雄盖世无对，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000011_e00012",
      "play_id": "80000011",
      "scene_id": "80000011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "哦，三弟来了！啊，三弟！你来呀……",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000011_e00013",
      "play_id": "80000011",
      "scene_id": "80000011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "太监"
      ],
      "text": "启主公：我那三千岁也不在人世了！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000011_e00014",
      "play_id": "80000011",
      "scene_id": "80000011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "哦，你那三千岁也不在人世了？",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000011_e00015",
      "play_id": "80000011",
      "scene_id": "80000011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
